      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-accepting-b" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The Thirteen Alpacas?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I'm glad you're here. Have you ever heard of the <FONT color=#a82424>Thirteen Alpacas</FONT> running in the <FONT color=#a82424>Blue Wind Plains</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
